title: Final Fantasy 11 XI Working Farm Bot
description:
This is a working farming bot for the online MMORPG Final Fantasy 11.

Last checked working on thursday, April &#039;08.

Simply run it before running POL viewer, set the settings seen on the program when loaded, and start farming. It is still a BETA, but works rather well.

NOTE: Will often not work on some systems when run after logging in, make sure the program is ran BEFORE starting POL viewer, and the bot is loaded, then you may log in.

Remember to seed!
